reviewText: Reminds me of sitting in the movie theater, all day on Saturday's when I was a kid, and just hoping there was a double feature on that day.......well it's not the same, believe me.......to see the actors and how fake it was really hit me. All one has to do, these days is buy a dvd filled with old black and white westerns, and watch them and they will make you really look at the movies today, with dolby surround sound, 55 to 60 inch H.D.  TV screens, and think "how in the world will the people in the next generation think about us, and how we survived. I think about it whenever I watch these old westerns......and wonder what John Wayne, Roy Rogers, Gene Autry would be thinking about seeing these movies like we're doing now........ummmmmmmmmm. So if you want to be entertained for a few hours just buy these westerns.....
Title: 10-Movie Western Pack, Vol. 2 Nothing Too Good For a Cowboy / Kid Vengeance / Cowboys Don't Cry / Pony Express Rider / Gun and the Pulpit / Death Rides a Horse / God's Gun / Ned's Blessing / Against Sky

reviewText: Sure they are older movies, and the film print isn't pristine, but for the money, it's great entertainment. People try to say the film quality isn't like todays films, but in 20 to 30 years, the newer films will be the same way these are. My wife and I really enjoyed, so much we ordered a couple of more different sets. Great westerns.
Title: 10-Movie Western Pack, Vol. 2 Nothing Too Good For a Cowboy / Kid Vengeance / Cowboys Don't Cry / Pony Express Rider / Gun and the Pulpit / Death Rides a Horse / God's Gun / Ned's Blessing / Against Sky
